overview:
Buzznab.com is a social networking service that allows members to create personal profiles in order to find and communicate with old and new friends.

It was created November, 2010 and launched in January, 2011. When visitors log into the site, they will immediately find lots of communication tools necessary to interact with each other via a member portal.

On Buzznab, members are allowed to listen to hundreds of live radio broadcasts, play games, create and share personal profile, videos, photo as well as accumulate points to win lots of prizes. BUZZNAB Points also let registered members to call ANY regular phone number worldwide for Free. As always on Buzznab you can enjoy FREE video calls, calls and live chat to other members.

Buzznab is been operated and managed by Prime Time Telecoms Inc a Japan based IP Telephony Service Provider.
